---
config:
  theme: neutral
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    box Agent
        participant Agent
    end

    box Local Scripts
        participant Init as cli_init
        participant Estado as cli_estado
        participant Clickup as cli_clickup
    end

    box Storage
        participant FS as Local FS
        participant Moodle
        participant API as ClickUp API
    end

    Note over Agent,API: === INIT FLOW ===

    Agent->>Init: gestionar-cursos init URL
    Init->>Moodle: scrape course page
    Moodle-->>Init: HTML (PGA table, sidebar)
    Init->>FS: create course folder, AGENTS.md, PGA.md
    Init->>FS: write clickup.json (folder/list = null)
    Init->>FS: create _cache/snapshot.json
    Init-->>Agent: course initialized

    Note over Agent,API: === SYNC PROMPT ===

    Agent->>Agent: ¿Sincronizar con ClickUp?
    Agent->>Clickup: cli_clickup.py PERIODO_DIR

    Note over Clickup,API: === CLICKUP SYNC ===

    Clickup->>FS: read clickup.json
    Clickup->>API: [1/3] find-or-create folder
    API-->>Clickup: folder.id

    loop each course in clickup.json
        Clickup->>API: [2/3] find-or-create list
        API-->>Clickup: list.id
        Clickup->>FS: update AGENTS.md CLICKUP_LIST_ID
        Clickup->>FS: update clickup.json list_id

        Clickup->>FS: read PGA.md
        loop each activity in PGA
            Clickup->>Clickup: classify (tags + priority)
            alt new task
                Clickup->>API: [3/3] create task
                API-->>Clickup: task.id
            else date changed
                Clickup->>API: [3/3] update task
                API-->>Clickup: ok
            else unchanged
                Note over Clickup: skip
            end
        end
    end

    Clickup->>FS: save updated clickup.json
    Clickup-->>Agent: sync complete

    Note over Agent,API: === LATER: ESTADO FLOW ===

    Agent->>Estado: estado CARPETA (auto or manual)
    Estado->>FS: load _cache/snapshot.json
    Estado->>Moodle: scrape sidebar
    Moodle-->>Estado: current activities

    Estado->>Estado: diff URLs (new | deleted | existing)

    par extract dates per unit
        Estado->>Moodle: quiz/assign dates (unit 1)
        Estado->>Moodle: quiz/assign dates (unit 2)
        Estado->>Moodle: quiz/assign dates (unit 3)
    end

    Estado->>Estado: diff dates vs snapshot
    Estado->>FS: save updated snapshot
    Estado-->>Agent: diff report

    Note over Agent,API: === RE-SYNC PROMPT ===

    Agent->>Agent: ¿Actualizar ClickUp?
    Agent->>Clickup: cli_clickup.py (creates new tasks, updates dates)
